This file describes the database structure for the Itea Online Store project.
The database name is the Iteashop. The database contains two tables,  users and products. The dump of  test dataset is in the iteashop.sql file.

users table description. 
6 fields
id (int) - counter auto-increment
login (varchar (50)) - user login (valid email)
password (varchar (100)) - Hashed user password
name (varchar (50)) - The display name of the user
region (varchar (50)) –– user region (area)
gender (bool) - gender (0 - female, 1 - male)
comment (varchar (200)) - any text

product table description.
5 fields
id (int) - counter auto-increment
name (varchar (50)) - the name of the product
description (text) - description of the product
price (int) - the price of the product
category (int) - product category (0 phones, 1- tablets, 2 - watches)
